{
  "texts": [
    "Clean data also simplifies the preparation of reports for audits, internal reviews, and regulatory bodies, ensuring transparency and accountability across food systems [198,199].",
    "(7) Resource optimization: Data cleaning and preprocessing help optimize resources by reducing the time and effort needed for manual data correction and analysis.",
    "Automated processes handle large data volumes efficiently, allowing food systems professionals to focus on higher-level strategic initiatives and decision-making [200,201].",
    "(8) Enhanced ML and AI: Many modern food safety management systems leverage ML and AI for predictive analytics and automated decision-making.",
    "These technologies require high-quality, preprocessed data to function effectively."
  ]
}